---
import Layout from "./layouts/Layout.astro";

const dossier = {
  callsign: "STARBOY CHAD",
  node: "STARBOYCHAD.COM",
  operation: "TALES FROM THE NEON WASTELAND",
  status: "ACTIVE",
  focus: ["Networking", "Security", "Cyberpunk 2077", "Fallout", "Immersion-First Storytelling"],
};

const body = `
I design and operate systems.

By day, that means real-world infrastructure. Networks, routing, segmentation, reliability and uptime. Systems that have to work, scale and recover under pressure.

By night, that same mindset gets applied to creative spaces: immersive game worlds, mod stacks, tooling, interfaces and experimental builds that prioritize intent, atmosphere, and cohesion.

Different environments. Same discipline.

This node started as a way to document heavily modified Cyberpunk 2077 and Fallout playthroughs, but it quickly became something more useful: a live demonstration of how I think, structure, troubleshoot and evolve complex systems.

Everything here reflects that approach:

Curated mod ecosystems instead of one-off installs

Interfaces designed to communicate state, not just look cool

Systems that degrade gracefully instead of breaking

Style layered on top of function. I never replace it

Games are just the medium.

Under the surface, this site is a working portfolio of:

Systems design

Network-aware thinking

Automation and tooling

UX decisions driven by signal, not noise

Creative problem-solving under constraint

This node will continue to grow.

Some projects will be fictional.
Some will be technical.
Some will blur the line completely.

If you’re here for the worlds, the stories, or the atmosphere...Welcome.
If you’re here to see how systems are built, connected and maintained...You’re already looking at the answer.

Operator online.
`;
---

<Layout title="About // StarboyChad.com">
  <section class="panel">
    <p class="kicker">OPERATOR FILE</p>
    <h1 class="title">About // {dossier.callsign}</h1>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <p class="label">NODE</p>
        <p class="value">{dossier.node}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="label">OPERATION</p>
        <p class="value">{dossier.operation}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="label">STATUS</p>
        <p class="value status">{dossier.status}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="label">FOCUS</p>
        <ul class="tags">
          {dossier.focus.map((t) => (
            <li class="tag">{t}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="copy">
      {body.split("\n").filter(Boolean).map((line) => (
        <p>{line}</p>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="ctaRow">
      <a class="btn cyan" href="/channels">Open Broadcast Node</a>
      <a class="btn pink" href="/modding">Access Modding Hub</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .panel{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 28px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .kicker{ font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.35em; opacity:0.7; text-transform:uppercase; margin:0 0 10px; }
    .title{ margin:0 0 18px; font-size: 28px; line-height:1.15; }

    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap:12px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .card{
      grid-column: span 6;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .card{ grid-column: span 12; }
    }

    .label{
      margin:0 0 6px;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      opacity: 0.65;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .value{
      margin:0;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .status{
      display:inline-block;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.35);
      background: rgba(34,211,238,0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,211,238,0.14);
    }

    .tags{
      list-style:none;
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:8px;
    }

    .tag{
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(232,121,249,0.30);
      background: rgba(232,121,249,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(232,121,249,0.10);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .divider{
      height:1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      margin: 18px 0 16px;
    }

    .copy p{
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      opacity: 0.90;
      max-width: 70ch;
    }

    .ctaRow{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration:none;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:0.22em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .btn:hover{ background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); }

    .cyan{ border-color: rgba(34,211,238,0.35); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(34,211,238,0.16); }
    .pink{ border-color: rgba(232,121,249,0.35); box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(232,121,249,0.14); }
  </style>
</Layout>
